    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-11-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-11-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="352" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d352">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Plumb</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 24.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-11-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 23, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> Your despatches Nos. 17 and 1S, of October
                            17th and 18th, respectively, have been received.</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * *</p>
                <pb facs="0552" n="482" xml:id="pg_482"/>
                <p>Upon a review of the whole matter, your refusal to place your indorsement
                            upon the paper presented to you by A. G. Farine, of the chancellerie of
                            the French legation, meets the approbation of this department.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Edward L Plumb,</hi> Esq., <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
